Simple CSS3 Path Selector

In this brave new world of using CSS3 path selectors rather than obtuse regular
expressions to parse our scraped & crawled HTML documents, you'd think there 
would be a bunch of decent online testing tools to help us out right?

Well I couldn't find any so here's a simple one which has no dependencies outside
of Perl & Mojolicious.

Online demo at http://mojo-css.herokuapp.com/